<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="按位或" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#按位或"><span>按位或</span></a></h3>
<p>按位或（OR）<code v-pre>|</code> 运算符与 <code v-pre>&amp;</code> 的区别在于如果对应的位中任一个操作数为 <code v-pre>1</code> 那么结果就是 <code v-pre>1</code>。</p>
