<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>简单记忆： 一个数与自身的取反值相加等于 <code v-pre>-1</code>。</p>
<h3 id="左移" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#左移"><span>左移</span></a></h3>
<p>左移（Left shift）<code v-pre>&lt;&lt;</code> 运算符使指定值的二进制数所有位都左移指定次数，其移动规则：<strong>丢弃高位，低位补 <code v-pre>0</code></strong>，即按二进制形式把所有的数字向左移动对应的位数，高位移出(舍弃)，低位的空位补零。</p>
